      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67745e34d9fb0.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6646e2338f909.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6646e233cb3e9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2736150.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2a91f17.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d295a71d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556aa1d3c4f6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f512adc45.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d275ec12.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65568b7d4c7bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2886007.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556905c98a47.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a43c437bc.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65539491ce10f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d29e262e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67744d2a13128.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6588ebe49c0f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f59c82d44.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f59d01b67.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a262b3208.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6556a5730e99c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/656e429b3151f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a0543b9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a286ac9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6553f5a014f02.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Crash Fixes + Other Improvements&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed crash instance in Eldin Sky region.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed a broken treasure chest on the Great Sky Island.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Golden Apples can now be eaten raw as intended.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Hylian Set upgrades adjusted to require intended material types and quantities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Improvement&lt;/em&gt;: TSQ's Enemy captions in the Compendium adjusted for length and formatting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Material captions in the Compendium updated to reflect changed descriptions in TSQ.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;Rediscover Hyrule Kingdom&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;Tears of the Kingdom: The Second Quest &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;is a large-scale mod being co-developed by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2343073"&gt;deadpanned&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2792161"&gt;YourDiamondDog&lt;/a&gt;, which remixes, rebalances, and reimagines many elements of Tears of the Kingdom to deliver an exciting New Game experience for veteran players or first-time players who favor a modded take on &lt;i&gt;The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom&lt;/i&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;It is strongly recommended to start a new save file for the best experience!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Features:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Combat Mechanics faithful to the game's core vision of a versatile physics-based combat system.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rebalanced Weapons and Materials to emphasize real-time tactics and more diverse fusion combinations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Diversified Enemies boasting new properties, greater intelligence, and stronger equipment all across Hyrule.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reworked World Scaling and Economy. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All-New Yiga Schematics and Schema Stones courtesy of &lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/HyruleEngineering/" target="_blank"&gt;The Hyrule Engineering Club&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Remixed Loot, Armor, and Legendary Weapon locations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Quest Rewards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;More challenging weather conditions across Hyrule, the Skies, and the Depths, including new underground biomes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Health Restoration System, further improved from &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472675"&gt;Cook or Die&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overhauled Armor System, further improved from&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/472574"&gt; Total Armor Rebalance&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional Armor Sets Improvable to raise defense or grant set bonuses.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Updated script including new loading screen tips, tutorial text, and NPC dialogue that matches changes to the mechanics and world. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quality of Life Elements and Unofficial Bug Fixes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;For a comprehensive list of changes and additions, see: &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1tCmZQIgrB6q_3_d2Y-j60kF1P9BliOjqW-wLIcjllV0/edit?gid=33460169#gid=33460169" target="_blank" class="SelectedElement"&gt;The Second Quest Spreadsheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Planned Features:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Localization for non-English languages.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shrine entrances remixed to lead to different shrines.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Additional Schematics optimized for 60 FPS compatibility.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mod Customization Options.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;...And More!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Compatibility Info:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Compatible game versions:&lt;b&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.1.2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.2.0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;1.2.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you have multiple mods that edit these files, use &lt;a href="https://github.com/TKMM-Team" target="_blank"&gt;TKMM (Tears of the Kingdom Mod Manager)&lt;/a&gt; to merge them:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ResourceSizeTable.Product.&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;110&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;121&lt;/span&gt;} file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;RSDB&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Mals&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Tag.Product&lt;/span&gt;.{&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;110&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;121&lt;/span&gt;} file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;GameDataList.Product.110.byml&lt;/span&gt; file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Banc&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Event&lt;/span&gt; folder files&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modifies the {&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Actor&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;.pack&lt;/span&gt; files for armor, weapons, food, enemies, Zonai devices, and the &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Player.pack&lt;/span&gt; file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Featured Engineers:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCThhMsHtYHWvd_jri49FInQ" target="_blank"&gt;2CPhoenix&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/BlazeAlchemist991/" target="_blank"&gt;BlazingAlchemist991&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@chesepuf" target="_blank"&gt;chesepuf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/BlazeAlchemist991/" target="_blank"&gt;Efficienct_Demand5759&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;FantasticPound&lt;br&gt;GoNinjaPro&lt;br&gt;LongJumpingFrame&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/ofstrings2/" target="_blank"&gt;OfStrings2&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@ofstrings2" target="_blank"&gt;Wood, Rubber, &amp;amp; Glue&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://on.soundcloud.com/ixGuV" target="_blank"&gt;OshKoshGanache&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Scared_Cry_4931/" target="_blank"&gt;SacredCry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Shak404/" target="_blank"&gt;Shak404&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Shlowpoke&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtube.com/@ytshotmaker" target="_blank"&gt;Shotmaker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/susannediazz/" target="_blank"&gt;Suusi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/Swapdoodle" target="_blank"&gt;Swapdoodle&lt;br&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Virama&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Ultrababouin/" target="_blank"&gt;Ultrababouin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Zhujzal&lt;br&gt;</description>
