or the continued support of my work. Even though I have no artistic talent, I still put a ton of work into getting these going and I have a ton more projects on the way!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Follow guide &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/tuts/16043"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; for help with installing mods on your preferred platform.</description>
