      <title>Horse Camping</title>
      <author>EzFastPaws</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/563938</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/563938#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">e22e12f5a65c4a61be1db9482feb83b307e7137e</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 22:12:20 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67688fb826b08.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67688bf4e5ba1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67688c22ad0ca.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Miss the opportunity to summon your horse from anywhere? Look no further!&lt;/h1&gt;(actually I don't mind, look anywhere you want)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;BotW introduced Ancient Bridle, with which you can summon your horse from anywhere with a whistle. Striving to replicate this experience, I made this mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Now you will have an ability to use the campfire to &lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;teleport your horse&lt;/b&gt;! The campfire works for version 1.2.1 and tries to understand any available language. It would work on any other versions older than 1.1.0 if I ask it nicely - so tell me if you need it!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;WARNING&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;: I left the mod functionality in the Depths, Sky Islands and Gerudo desert (since I don't know how not to). But the game&lt;i&gt; really&lt;/i&gt; doesn't like the idea of horses being there and does wild things to any living horse who somehow gets to these places (study the following botw vid:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j3UCeodYq7w&amp;amp;ab_channel=Linkums%28WhatTheyCallGames%29" target="_blank"&gt;Riding a horse in the desert in Breath of the Wild? - YouTube&lt;/a&gt;). The horse will be fine - trust me, I tested these teleportation cases. But it won't like this, so please get a good care of your friend's wellbeing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Afterword&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;b&gt;TKMM&lt;/b&gt; friendly reminder - remember to set the appropriate language in Settings&amp;gt;Merging&amp;gt;Target Language.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I make mistakes, so if you encounter a problem - message me on discord &lt;u&gt;ezfastpaws&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ah, oh, and... &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Marry&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Christmas&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Happy&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;New&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Year!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;</description>
