    <item>
      <title>Super Speed Stable</title>
      <author>charlie92155</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/559144</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/559144#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">205609ece1f01f8e5f6606e175fdeb4c7d6ab560</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 17:08:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676884c6bcb2e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6749e5a88d92a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6749e5a8a4b65.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Added Mounts&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;LinIX's new Zonai Capsule has a renamed Nushi Actor, so I added it as well as increasing the speed of the  Sand Seal. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added Sand Seal&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Added Another Nushi Depths Variant&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Do you miss zooming through hyrule on your motorcyle? Well what if you can go faster than a mastercycle?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a partial port of my old &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/410742"&gt;Botw Mod&lt;/a&gt;.  I dramatically increased the speed of my favorite horses.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There are two versions, a &lt;b&gt;very fast one&lt;/b&gt;, and a &lt;b&gt;very very fast one&lt;/b&gt;. In the &lt;u&gt;very very&lt;/u&gt; fast one donkeys are tad slower (same speed as the &lt;u&gt;very fast&lt;/u&gt; horses in the other version). &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;This mod will make these animals virtually impossible to catch on foot without some kind of elemental assistance.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Horses:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Epona&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Zelda's White Horse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Zelda's Gold Horse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Giant Black Horse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nushi&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;*All Day Stal Horse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;*Nushi (Depths Version)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;*Donkeys &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Sand Seal&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;*If you really want to take advantage of the Stal, Nushi Depths Version, and Donkeys they will require the the following mods as contingencies.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Contingencies&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;LinlX's &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/558837"&gt;Satori &amp; Stalhorse &amp; Large Zonai Platform Capsules&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;HGStone's &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/508409"&gt;Ride the Donkeys&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Works with  Versions 1.1.0 - 1.2.1&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
